p: I hereby certify that I saved the within Summond and annexed Complaint on the within named Defendent W.H. Barrett of Walla Walla County in Said Teritory on the 10th day of August A.D. 1873 by Delivering to him personally time copies of the Sam Certified to the book by W. H. Andrews Clerk of the District Court of the first Judicial district of Washington Teritory this 1st Day of September 1873
